# Rendered daily-video media (large binaries) — the .md scripts and the
# paste-ready .youtube.txt stay tracked; the rendered audio/video do not.
# The final MP4 is delivered out-of-band (Telegram / ~/Local/ikigai), not via git.
content/data/video-scripts/*.mp4
content/data/video-scripts/*.mp3
content/data/video-scripts/*.wav
